INTRODUCTION :
this module will manage the themes of your web site by reading the tree of the var/themes and
modifing the defaultcofig.ini.php file to store the choosen theme

PREREQUISITES :
module master_admin

INSTALLATION :
- Copy the hfnuthemes directory in your backoffice side (in the modules directory)
- run the install.mysql.sql SQL script to add the expected rights
if you use prefix to your table name, modify the install.mysql.sql script and add your prefix.

that's all!

the module will respond to the Events of the master_module to display itself